								"id": "tqq24I9NJrLajsURv"
							},
							"name": "Code of Honor (Pirate's)",
							"reference": "B127",
							"local_notes": "Always avenge an insult, regardless of the danger; your buddy’s foe is your own; never attack a fellow crewman or buddy except in a fair, open duel.",
